node.text: Okay guys I have always believed transparency is the best way to go. So here goes...I was honestly equally upset about the launch of @jolieandjace because I want the line to be affordable AND quality. Our first run we had someone hand sewing which made the prices way higher.  We have been able to switch manufacturers due to high demand therefore lower costs AND SAME GREAT QUALITY!  so tomorrow we launch the new prices. $30 off on the cozy set!! In the new year I will be making more pieces and will find other materials to create even lower cost pieces so everyone is happy because I want us all to be cozy. ALSO. We have been able to size up to size 18. I will work very hard to continue to be more inclusive in sizes in the new year. I want us to all be cozy and happy. SHOP TOMORROW AT 9am PACIFIC!!!! I’m excited to grow this line with more styles and cozy in 2021 with y’all!  P.s. for the people that bought the first round, check your inbox in the next few days...got something for you;)

node.text:
Love finding my new go to bras and since y’all ask where I get them from, this one is from @somaintimates AND on sale!  Also their p-jay sets are so comfy! 

These pajama shorts are part of the cool nights pajamas set and they’re my new absolute favorites!! I always get sooooo hot when I sleep so these are a game changer! (apparently this is normal and at least 40% of women have trouble sleeping because they get too hot and sweaty, who knew 🤷🏻‍♀️)

But the best part is this Enbliss bra which is also so super comfy!  I can’t wear underwire bras now, so these are PERFECT!  They don’t have any wires, the material is super soft and it still offers the support that we all need.

And because I just love these bras so much, I wanted to make sure and share an amazing sale they’re having right now through midnight on 8/16!  @somaintimates is hosting a 3 for $99 bra sale that includes almost all Soma bras (some exclusions). Their bras usually start around $50 so getting 3 for $99 is an amazing deal!! Head to my stories for the swipe up link and gets yours now! #somastartswithme
